data.description: CORNER LOT! Welcome to this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the beautiful, quiet community in Hudson. This spacious, elevated lot is one of the biggest in the neighborhood and is in a no flood zone, despite being situated only minutes away from the water. The yard has enough room for new owners to add additions! The recent upgrades include a new roof, gutters, and garage door all replaced in 2023, and the disposal replaced in 2020. As you enter, you’re welcomed by the homey family room that includes a mounted 86” screen TV and seamlessly connects with the kitchen and dining area, making it great for hosting! The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, such as a Samsung fridge and dishwasher. Step inside to the master bedroom where you’ll find a  75” mounted screen TV and walk in closet. Enjoy the secluded sunroom that offers an abundance of windows and plenty of sunlight that could be utilized as an office or playroom. Clubhouse includes a range of facilities like a swimming pool, shuffleboard, and playground. Conveniently located close to shopping and restaurants and walking trails. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this wonderful home yours!
